            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大跌1.03%，報4909.71點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間15日09:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>下跌51.02點（或1.03%），暫報4909.71點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+13.09%</li><li>近 1 月：+23.92%</li><li>近 3 月：-3.88%</li><li>近 6 月：-0.88%</li><li>今年以來：-0.39%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)領跌。萊迪思半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:LSCC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/LSCC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">LSCC-US</a>)下跌1.75%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)下跌1.66%；英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)下跌1.51%；邁威爾科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MRVL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MRVL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MRVL-US</a>)下跌1.41%；應用材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)下跌1.35%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲4.93%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲2.28%；高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)上漲1.08%；艾司摩爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASML:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASML\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASML-US</a>)上漲0.66%；安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)上漲0.2%。</p></section></main>",
