            "title": "盤中速報 - 迪爾(DE-US)大漲5.3%，報523.87美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)截至台北時間15日21:30股價上漲26.37美元，報523.87美元，漲幅5.3%，成交量81,300（股），盤中最高價524.54美元、最低價517.35美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.43%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.32%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.67%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.05%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.31%</li> <li>近 1 月：+6.38%</li> <li>近 3 月：+3.6%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.06%</li> <li>今年以來：+17.42%</li></ul></section></main>",
